+ (void) registerCoder: (Class)  coder
objectType: (Class)  type
mimeTypes: (NSArray *)  mimeTypes 

Register a coder class to handle a particular object type (like NSString) or a collection of mime-types (like text/plain).

Parameters:
mimeTypes - an Array of either NSString or NSRegularExpression objects to match against header values. Strings must match exactly.
